<title>
<sentence type="quasi">ＰＯＩＮＴ　１</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence type="quasi">あいさつと会話</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</title>
<sentence type="quasi">この基本を実行すれば関係がグッとよくなる</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
